40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"899dfa8099a314f8a7ee24e2be23870d8831285b","tid":208980,"uid":90505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T11:30:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你會有好多時間唔知佢做緊咩<br />\n溝通少左好多<br />\n大部份時間好似單身咁<br />\n對要有好大自由度嘅人係一件好開心嘅事</blockquote><br />\n咁唔岩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係返shift 果個，佢話覺得唔了解我，少左溝通，距離愈黎愈遠<br />\n我返工佢放假，我放假佢返工，覺得我無時間take care佢<br />\n利申：手已分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n少咗溝通呢個真心難搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcc2de3a3c9c646fc68922d5b360a7562d4d259c","tid":208980,"uid":90505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T11:33:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同男朋友都係咁樣<br />\n未試過因爲呢樣野嗌交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家就下 你接下佢收工佢接下你收工咁囉</blockquote><br />\n夜媽媽仲要山卡啦咁遠都幾難做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d0cb981f96eadf83cea1d8077f982701cd8795","tid":208980,"uid":90505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T11:34:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>散梗<br />\n陪唔到佢 佢大把時間俾人溝</blockquote><br />\n你唔夠上心 人地既介入<br />\n有咗比較 的確有爭執既機會都大好多"}]}